/\" target=\"_blank\">повече</a></p>\r\n', 'Yes', 500),
(57, 2, 'Administration', '', '<h1 style=\"color:#333; font-family:Verdana, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n	Student Office:</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:Verdana, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; color:#606060;\">\r\n	<strong>Office hours:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"font-family: Verdana, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(96, 96, 96);\">\r\n		from 10:00 to 12:00 a.m</li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-family: Verdana, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(96, 96, 96);\">\r\n		from 13:00 to 15:00 p.m</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"color:#333; font-family:Verdana, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n	Inspectors:</h2>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"6\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family:Verdana, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:13px; color:#606060;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n				<b>Ani Kocheva</b><br />\r\n				Email: <a href=\"mailto:ak@tu-sofia.bg\" style=\"color:#0000cc; text-decoration:none;\">ak@tu-sofia.bg</a><br />\r\n				Room: 1327<br />\r\n				Phone: 02 965 3139</td>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family:Verdana, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:13px; color:#606060;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n				<b>M.Sc. Eng. Daniela Bocheva-Yancheva</b><br />\r\n				Email: <a href=\"mailto:dbocheva@tu-sofia.bg\" style=\"color:#0000cc; text-decoration:none;\">dbocheva@tu-sofia.bg</a><br />\r\n				Room: 1322-A<br />\r\n				Phone.: 02 965 2054</td>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family:Verdana, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:13px; color:#606060;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n				<b>Samira Aliman</b><br />\r\n				Email: <a href=\"mailto:samira@tu-sofia.bg\" style=\"color:#0000cc; text-decoration:none;\">samira@tu-sofia.bg</a><br />\r\n				Room: 1322-A<br />\r\n				Phone: 02 965 2054</td>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family:Verdana, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:13px; color:#606060;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n				<b>M.Sc. Eng. Rositsa Georgieva</b><br />\r\n				Email: <a href=\"mailto:georgieva.rosy@tu-sofia.bg\" style=\"color:#0000cc; text-decoration:none;